{"tid":895880,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[提醒身邊既朋友小心中伏]  斜坡範圍特大 逸璟‧龍灣業主須自費保養","createTime":"2018-11-09T14:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T07:33:27.000Z","uid":59746,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"5074f5ec9bca550abd6e89f14f42f0269b2dfc83","tid":895880,"uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2205074/%E6%96%9C%E5%9D%A1%E7%AF%84%E5%9C%8D%E7%89%B9%E5%A4%A7%20%E9%80%B8%E7%92%9F%E2%80%A7%E9%BE%8D%E7%81%A3%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E9%A0%88%E8%87%AA%E8%B2%BB%E4%BF%9D%E9%A4%8A?mtc=90025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2205074%2F%25E6%2596%259C%25E5%259D%25A1%25E7%25AF%2584%25E5%259C%258D%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25A4%25A7%2520%25E9%2580%25B8%25E7%2592%259F%25E2%2580%25A7%25E9%25BE%258D%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25A0%2588%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%25A4%258A%3Fmtc%3D90025&d=SNJlKeDMB3Z0KcbjhlF8%2FttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=320c901a\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2205074/%E6%96%9C%E5%9D%A1%E7%AF%84%E5%9C%8D%E7%89%B9%E5%A4%A7%20%E9%80%B8%E7%92%9F%E2%80%A7%E9%BE%8D%E7%81%A3%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E9%A0%88%E8%87%AA%E8%B2%BB%E4%BF%9D%E9%A4%8A?mtc=90025</a><br />\n<br />\n國企的中冶置業進軍香港一手市場，首個住宅新盤荃灣西逸璟‧龍灣首批50伙已開價，屋苑坐落青山公路青龍頭段108號，依山而建，鄰近大型屋苑豪景花園，逸璟‧龍灣由兩座16層高物業組成，涉198伙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2205000/2205074/A01_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2205000%2F2205074%2FA01_1024.png&h=6dd2dbca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣的準買家應花時間留意樓書資料，根據樓書內「斜坡維修」一項，指明批地文件規定發展項目內業主須自費保養斜坡的費用，列明有關保養所進行工程的費用構成管理開支的一部分，由業主支付，並相應地可向業主收回。而據附設的圖片所見，項目後面有護土牆及斜坡，其中護土牆的範圍面積比發展項目面積還要大。<br />\n<br />\n地產站向有關發展商方面查詢項目預計管理費資料，獲回覆暫未公開。<br />\n<br />\n除了斜坡維修方面，買家亦要留意項目單位設有不少減低噪音的設備，如固定玻璃、維修窗口、縱向隔音鰭等，分布客飯廳及睡房等。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母中國野真係冇好死<br />\n分分鐘6球野買完樓要再比2球整"},{"pid":"e888bee006b484630479050e47e77e8efa92d8c3","tid":895880,"uid":62935,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:21:37.000Z","msg":"呢個時候踢爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92ffcf9065f65d240f85efb32d08eee5bf91dc9","tid":895880,"uid":27766,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:23:06.000Z","msg":"呢個位啲人叫荃灣西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3733bd7cff03c4f16156a2d15519861097e9f71","tid":895880,"uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"管理費一定貴到hihi, 個斜坡仲大過個樓盤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f27589eb4d8ea86ac07707c4e354a3e39f89cfc","tid":895880,"uid":59746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:36:14.000Z","msg":"痴撚線直頭要比錢整護土坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仼人劏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60df88bc037929586b7ecccb33e386abaa8a63b","tid":895880,"uid":34013,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:43:59.000Z","msg":"仲入過深井叫荃灣西  屯門叫荃灣西西丫笨"},{"pid":"8bd8a47bee37e1221716abb7d5b6871ea6146d34","tid":895880,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a60df88bc037929586b7ecccb33e386abaa8a63b","tid":895880,"uid":34013,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:43:59.000Z","msg":"仲入過深井叫荃灣西  屯門叫荃灣西西丫笨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"大圍都叫九龍塘啦"},{"pid":"6074721fce47cc9d8e3dc40b3a33f3b0ed3f8fd6","tid":895880,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:24:05.000Z","msg":"明明係青龍頭/身井<br />\n<br />\n利申：跑步成日經過"},{"pid":"9240e1b0464debe3918de68e1d9c3aa22429e2a2","tid":895880,"uid":84633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6074721fce47cc9d8e3dc40b3a33f3b0ed3f8fd6","tid":895880,"ui